HEADWORD: Transcribe
<hw>Tran*scribe"</hw> <pr>(tr⟦acr⟧n*skr⟦imac⟧b")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>Transcribed</conjf>
<pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Transcribing</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[L. <ets>transcribere</ets>,
